      </div>
      <div class="content">
        <h2 class="text-center">Activate Your Account</h2>
        <p>Thank you for joining Picverse! We're excited to have you as part of our creative community.</p>
        <p>
          To complete your registration and start exploring amazing content, please click the button below to activate your
          account:
        </p>
        <a href="{{activateUrl}}" class="button">Activate Account</a>
        <p>
          This activation link will expire in 24 hours for security reasons. If you didn't create an account, you can safely
          ignore this email.
        </p>
        <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, don't hesitate to reach out to our support team.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer">
        <p>The Picverse Team</p>
        <p>If you didn't create an account, please <a href="#">contact support</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>